# Use Repository Skills First

Before implementing tasks, read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root and choose the matching project skill from `.cursor/skills/`.

Apply the documented workflow order by default:
1. `pnpm run logs:sync:site` (when logs/process artifacts are in scope)
2. `pnpm run build:site`
3. `pnpm run test:e2e:site`
4. Deploy only when explicitly requested

Never commit secrets (`.env`, tokens), and ensure log redaction checks when publishing transcripts.
